      <h3>IPRA Is On The Move </h3> 
      <p>
       Recently, a decision has been made to move the IPRA Headquarters to a new location. This will allow for future advancements in all areas of membership.</p>
      <p>The IPRA Board of Directors has instructed staff to pursue alternative sites for the association offices to maximize resources to better serve its members. IPRA has created this site as a central repository for all members to view information relevant to this topic. </p>
